items.title: Nasdaq Composite, Dow Jones fall as weak earnings weigh on sentiment
items.description: The major indexes are on course to end the week lower, with markets set to remain shut on Friday for Good Friday. The S&P 500 is down more than 1 percent so far this week, while the Dow and Nasdaq have lost nearly 3 percent each.
